Metadata.Title: Vamping In Paris
Metadata.Description: The Vampire Magician is hungry! Quench your bloodlust by murdering the four guards that the ghoul has been eyeing for some time. You'll need a prime cut for the main course, not to mention a new bride to dine with... but make haste! Return back to your lair to rest once the deed is done - you'll only have a limited amount of time before your appetite succumbs you...
